e.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1ChSolNzpiX0HE8IUGJ8-Cl6A3so_8wgn&h=784d2e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nG.E.M.今次唔着皮褲，仲展現性感一面！<br />\n<br />\n歌手鄧紫棋（G.E.M.）對時裝有獨特喜好，以往都畀好多驚喜大家，除咗老是常皮褲，仲有窗簾布、尿片褲、蟲蟲裝等等，每次都驚為天人！G.E.M.今日又出動喇，但今次就唔再着皮褲改玩成熟，佢大玩See Through誘惑，長裙盤骨及大髀位置透出一大片，內裏嘅T-Back若隱若現，鬼死咁惹火！<br />\n<br />\n佢留言：「裙子的亮點請自行尋找」再加埋猴子掩面emoji，怕怕醜醜咁，網友都留言激讚性感「看到了底褲」，仲不忘提醒佢小心走光呀！而佢呢個咁特別嘅造型，就係出自造型師男友Mark手筆，唔知大家又buy唔buy呢？<br />\n<br />\n另外，同G.E.M.一齊參加大陸綜藝節目《中國新說唱》嘅吳亦凡特登喺洛杉磯帶咗花生醬畀佢，仲三瓶咁多添！G.E.M.上載兩人合照，笑言「夠吃起碼三個月」！ <br />\n<br />\n來源 source: <a href=\"http://hk.on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc&d=2NKyO7fI0FiLhX2dfX1LHMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=002bd329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc</a><br />\n<br />\n+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++<br />\n<br />\n玩邊料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67971c18765e8759a08a6d87cae6432b8388c549","tid":843211,"uid":132587,"like":375,"dislike":10,"score":365,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:36:36.000Z","msg":"果陣蝗味原來唔係天生 係可以日積月累番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e650f16632c3eaf2651f9eb148ae7deb94e102","tid":843211,"uid":52605,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:44:20.000Z","msg":"對波縮咗水"},{"pid":"e0d80cd40c95d48f5224a15c23bcf8d755b4d9d5","tid":843211,"uid":167780,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:46:01.000Z","msg":"佢塊面真係削左啲咁"},{"pid":"50f14b3f7953dd059752b60fe1a1f7ad528c1316","tid":843211,"uid":40789,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:46:12.000Z","msg":"搵錢搵到自已都墮落晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71019ea9fb056d2da62568ddf7b4b1ca9a67e412","tid":843211,"uid":20448,"like":124,"dislike":5,"score":119,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:48:11.000Z","msg":"條吳亦凡真係好撚大陸哩<img src=\"/ass